match.name: 3 Mile Creek PRS Steel Challenge
match.about:
Payment Info
Venmo @Aaron-Brown-7
Match Fee $50
Please put your full name and date of match in comments, this will help me keep track of payments better.
You will not be able to shoot match if you do not pay prior to the match date.

Please select the appropriate Division

Three Mile Creek Shooting Range
Location 3100 South 2015 West 
Perry, UT 84302
https://www.perrycityut.gov/three-mile-creek-gun-range.htm

Match Director Aaron Brown
This will be the first time directing a PRS match. 
However, I have directed 12 other Long range matches. 

I will be using Impact Scoring to score the match, so I will need 1 or 2 squad members with impact scoring on their phones so they can score for their squad. 

Gate will open up at 7:30 am, you will be able to zero from 7:30 am to 8:30 am. 
You cannot shoot any steel at this time but can shoot any dirt berm.

We will start the safety briefing and stage walk through at 8:30 am. Match will start after.

Round count will be 80-90 rounds.
Target Distances 300-1000 Yards

You will not be able to shoot match if you do not pay prior to the match date.

For any questions or to arrange alternate payment you can text or Email me.
801-814-7638
mistyabe@gmail.com
Aaron Brown
